 in the regression of 
\begin_inset Formula $w_{\nu}$
\end_inset

 merely indicates the differences in prices
\begin_inset Formula $P_{\nu}(A)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{\nu}(A')$
